msgid ""
"Runnable Klein for Ray examples for bounded pipelines, streaming state, "
"SQL, and event time."
msgstr "可运行的 Klein for Ray 示例，涵盖有界管道、流式状态、SQL 和事件时间。"

msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

msgid ""
"The examples use public `ray.klein` APIs and run from the project root "
"after you install the package."
msgstr "这些示例使用公共 `ray.klein` API。安装软件包后，可从项目根目录运行它们。"

msgid "Run the quick start"
msgstr "运行快速入门示例"

msgid ""
"The quick start creates a bounded pipeline, attaches a collection sink, "
"and retrieves its rows from the completed job handle:"
msgstr "快速入门示例创建一个有界管道，挂接集合 sink，并从已完成的作业句柄中取回记录："

msgid "examples/quick_start.py"
msgstr "examples/quick_start.py"

msgid "Run it with:"
msgstr "运行命令如下："

msgid "Run batch SQL"
msgstr "运行批处理 SQL"

msgid "examples/sql_batch.py"
msgstr "examples/sql_batch.py"

msgid "Run managed state on a finite streaming source"
msgstr "在有限流式源上运行托管状态"

msgid "examples/stateful_streaming.py"
msgstr "examples/stateful_streaming.py"

msgid ""
"This example explicitly selects streaming because managed keyed state has"
" no Ray Data batch lowering. The finite collection source reaches end-of-"
"data, the job completes, and ``JobHandle.get()`` returns the collected "
"rows."
msgstr "此示例显式选择 streaming，因为托管键控状态无法下沉为 Ray Data 批处理。有限集合源到达数据末尾后，作业完成，``JobHandle.get()`` 返回收集到的记录。"

msgid "Explore feature examples"
msgstr "探索功能示例"

msgid ""
"The guides include focused examples next to the behavior they explain. "
"Code containing placeholders or external URIs is illustrative; the "
"standalone files under `examples/` are the smoke-tested local examples."
msgstr "各指南会在所解释的行为旁提供针对性示例。包含占位符或外部 URI 的代码仅用于说明；`examples/` 下的独立文件才是经过冒烟测试的本地示例。"

msgid ""
"[Production streaming walkthrough](production-streaming.md) provides one "
"complete Kafka, watermark, window, checkpoint, file-sink, CLI, and "
"restore path and states all external prerequisites."
msgstr ""
"[生产环境流处理实战](production-streaming.md)提供一条涵盖 Kafka、水位线、窗口、检查点、文件 sink、CLI "
"和恢复的完整路径，并列出所有外部前置条件。"

msgid ""
"[Ray Data interoperability](ray-data-interop.md) shows native Dataset "
"transforms and multi-stream dependencies."
msgstr "[Ray Data 互操作性](ray-data-interop.md)演示原生 Dataset 转换和多流依赖。"

msgid ""
"[Connector catalog](connectors/index.md) includes runnable setup examples"
" for Kafka, filesystems, Redis, collections, console, custom connectors, "
"and Ray Serve."
msgstr ""
"[连接器目录](connectors/index.md)包含 Kafka、文件系统、Redis、集合、控制台、自定义连接器和 Ray Serve "
"的可运行配置示例。"

msgid ""
"[SQL and Table connectors](sql.md) shows caller-scope tables, temporary "
"views, joins, aggregates, and connector DDL."
msgstr "[SQL 和 Table 连接器](sql.md)演示调用方作用域表、临时视图、连接、聚合和连接器 DDL。"

msgid ""
"[Managed state](ray-native-state.md) shows a keyed running total and "
"event-time windows."
msgstr "[托管状态](ray-native-state.md)演示键控累计值和事件时间窗口。"

msgid ""
"[Event time](event-time.md) shows bounded-out-of-orderness watermarks and"
" idle-input detection."
msgstr "[事件时间](event-time.md)演示有限乱序水位线和空闲输入检测。"

msgid ""
"Connector and production examples state whether they require a bounded "
"source, a streaming source, or an external service."
msgstr "连接器和生产环境示例会说明其是否需要有界源、流式源或外部服务。"
